Use the "Update" button when you want to update the platform with the latest configuration saved in Studio.

The Update button will update, on this Nuxeo instance, the version of your package with a new snapshot that includes the latest configuration generated by Studio.
Most of the features configured in Studio do not need the server to be restarted, so you will be able to test immediately the changes you made.
However, the development mode needs to be activated first.
